          "message": "feat(docs): custom theme, mascot branding, and favicon (#15)\n\n* feat: setup VitePress docs for GitHub Pages deployment\n\n- Rename config.ts to config.mts (ESM compatibility)\n- Add base: '/kruda/' for GitHub Pages path\n- Add sidebar sections: contrib, AI integration, migration guides\n- Update hero tagline and features on landing page\n- Add docs/guide/ai-integration.md (MCP setup guide)\n- Add docs/guide/contrib.md (10 contrib modules)\n- Add workflow_dispatch trigger to docs workflow\n- Merge benchmark charts from gh-pages into docs build\n- Add package-lock.json for CI reproducibility\n- Switch GitHub Pages from branch to Actions deployment\n\n* feat(docs): add custom theme, mascot branding, and favicon",
